{"tid":2191630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網媒記者旺角被票控違限聚令　警稱記者證沒登記拒豁免","createTime":"2020-09-06T14:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:48:52.000Z","uid":5312,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"555cbf29166257f17ee58bbbeaa2c19879fa239b","tid":2191630,"uid":5312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"警方晚上繼續在旺角進行截查，進入西洋菜南街一間電子用品連鎖店，帶走店內部份人，有網媒記者被票控違反「限聚令」。<br />\n<br />\n警員晚上在電子用品連鎖店外拉起封鎖線，其後進入店內，逐一檢查店內市民的身份證和隨身物品，當中包括穿著寫有「急救」字樣背心的人，部分人其後被帶出店外，警員用索帶將他們雙手反綁，約兩小時後陸續帶走。<br />\n<br />\n警方截查期間，一名女士不適，獲警員安排坐在路旁，有警員上前協助，讓她解開索帶和聞氧氣。在封鎖該店約1個多小時後，店舖職員拉閘後離開店鋪。<br />\n<br />\n晚上約8時半，警方又向山東街方向推進，在該處截查車輛，警員用電筒照射車廂，又檢查外賣電單車的保溫袋。<br />\n<br />\n網媒「Free HK」記者吳小姐表示，她與2名同事從後巷走出豉油街，有警員指向他們，表示他們違反「限聚令」，警員檢視他們的記者證後，指其所屬機構並沒有在新聞處登記，因此不獲豁免。她說，會到法庭抗辯，不會繳交罰款。她的同事就表示，不同意由警方判斷他們是否記者，強調不會繳交罰款。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548190-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548190-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4lT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=1b343e50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548190-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=39bf6a21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548190-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7d54759c1f815c221e1a789f7a815775b113f2f6","tid":2191630,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警員檢視他們的記者證後，指其所屬機構並沒有在新聞處登記，因此不獲豁免。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何時有呢條規則?"},{"pid":"d45d92a40de3c5b0668541f209d8af00613e4c3e","tid":2191630,"uid":5312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d54759c1f815c221e1a789f7a815775b113f2f6","tid":2191630,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警員檢視他們的記者證後，指其所屬機構並沒有在新聞處登記，因此不獲豁免。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何時有呢條規則?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"黑警:我話唔計就唔計"},{"pid":"e8b443a0f7ba997a7af4abd32a0ae62da4d7df4d","tid":2191630,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"黑警依家擺明鏡頭前犯法，反正律政司會保"},{"pid":"967736a83e669e627d3e0fcaefeab1ad02ecbcf6","tid":2191630,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"唔好搞亂香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527589f4722ff89737874fca9543b4b588d7990a","tid":2191630,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d54759c1f815c221e1a789f7a815775b113f2f6","tid":2191630,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警員檢視他們的記者證後，指其所屬機構並沒有在新聞處登記，因此不獲豁免。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n何時有呢條規則?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"有咩同官講"},{"pid":"3a9dec99e607e46ac7e4c3eeaf5f1882d3584f81","tid":2191630,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"香港有新聞自由？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691f5ca68e1dc75e5b30f415d2163080d12883a3","tid":2191630,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"林奠幾時出黎講香港其實係無新聞自由？"},{"pid":"a432b42a79468b9e6b725008d14ed3a7f1020d39","tid":2191630,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"屌你 咪唔撚交囉<br />\n<br />\n你咪出夠100張告票囉"},{"pid":"3cb1a8826fc08cc973e1169ff740cbe15e928dec","tid":2191630,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"佢地手上份認可list 只有大公文匯東方cctvb"}]}